a:9:{s:5:"title";s:69:"5分钟带你穿越17年青春回忆，SHE这次可赚足了眼泪！";s:7:"content";s:45429:"<p><span style="font-size: 14px;">SHE终于又合体发新歌了，这几天O姐的心情简直比过年还开心。</span></p>
<p><br></p>
<p><img class="" data-backh="408" data-backw="558" data-before-oversubscription-url="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/JFguiaeP3xaRZIjTYTuf4lQvcBNTG44pCEkWibt6Oic5Pn13F9XialmcXRm3FINk5oox6dibPMP0bzZgr09M3Owtx4w/0?wx_fmt=gif" data-ratio="0.7316666666666667" style="width:100%;height:auto" src="http://192.168.3.19:8900/api/base/imgproxy?1=1&siteid=1&url=https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/JFguiaeP3xaRZIjTYTuf4lQvcBNTG44pCEkWibt6Oic5Pn13F9XialmcXRm3FINk5oox6dibPMP0bzZgr09M3Owtx4w/640?wx_fmt=gif" data-type="gif" data-w="600" style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);display: block;width: 100%;height: auto;"></p>
<p><br></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 14px;">9月的第一天，SHE在网易云音乐上公开发布了全新单曲《十七》。单曲海报上，三个人身穿白色长裙站在蓝色的篮球场上，脸上没有了十七年前稚嫩，取而代之的经过岁月打磨之后的成熟韵味。</span></p>
<p><br></p>
<p><img class="" data-backh="841" data-backw="558" data-before-oversubscription-url="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/JFguiaeP3xaRZIjTYTuf4lQvcBNTG44pC6CNFjEOibJmdDTf10ic2aaW4haz8GY0EkMxibp8V0mricTu7xB2MwLnYBQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="1.5066666666666666" style="width:100%;height:auto" src="http://192.168.3.19:8900/api/base/imgproxy?1=1&siteid=1&url=https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/JFguiaeP3xaRZIjTYTuf4lQvcBNTG44pC6CNFjEOibJmdDTf10ic2aaW4haz8GY0EkMxibp8V0mricTu7xB2MwLnYBQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="600" style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);display: block;width: 100%;height: auto;"></p>
<p><br></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 14px;">9月7日，在SHE成团十七周年之际，《十七》的官方MV也正式跟我们见面了。MV真实地还原了三个人从无人识的选秀咖一路走到现在的艰辛历程，简直就是一发催泪弹。</span></p>
<p><br></p>
<p><iframe class="video_iframe" data-vidtype="2" data-cover="http://192.168.3.19:8900/api/base/imgproxy?1=1&siteid=1&url=http%3A%2F%2Fshp.qpic.cn%2Fqqvideo_ori%2F0%2Fp07791knw4u_496_280%2F0" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" data-ratio="1.7777777777777777" data-w="864" src="https://v.qq.com/iframe/preview.html?width=500&amp;height=375&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=p07791knw4u"></iframe></p>
<section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section class="V5" style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;padding-left: 6px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="background-color: rgb(255, 129, 36);padding-right: 6px;padding-left: 6px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">意料之外的爆红</strong></p></section><section style="margin-top: -9px;margin-left: -6px;border-left: 2px solid rgb(13, 0, 21);border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(13, 0, 21);height: 16px;width: 16px;border-top-color: rgb(13, 0, 21);border-right-color: rgb(13, 0, 21);box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section></section></section></section><p><br></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 14px;">MV的第一幕，就把我们拉回了2000年的9月。</span></p>
<p><br></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="" data-copyright="0" data-ratio="0.54421768707483" style="width:100%;height:auto" src="http://192.168.3.19:8900/api/base/imgproxy?1=1&siteid=1&url=https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/JFguiaeP3xaRZIjTYTuf4lQvcBNTG44pCVGr9BHhQjIK8ziceVjbjxGibtJKr7XwrvaBh9L1X6haEiba9BlOUeNAEA/640?wx_fmt=gif" data-type="gif" data-w="441" style=""></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 14px;">三个人因为一档名为《宇宙2000实力美少女争霸战》的选秀节目聚在一起，然后被当时的宇宙音乐也就是现在的华研国际看中并签约出道。</span></p>
<p><br></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="" data-copyright="0" data-ratio="0.54421768707483" style="width:100%;height:auto" src="http://192.168.3.19:8900/api/base/imgproxy?1=1&siteid=1&url=https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/JFguiaeP3xaRZIjTYTuf4lQvcBNTG44pCg5VUEWgib4WIvhu9cBytdjxmPibyCQtdBjnzr9R9oHciaFB3gRuAlNO9A/640?wx_fmt=gif" data-type="gif" data-w="441" style=""></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 14px;">从参加比赛到后来出道，她们从来都没觉得自己会红。毕竟三个人当初来参加比赛的原因也都不是为了当明星，Selina任家萱是由于妹妹任容萱年龄小无法参加这个比赛，所以她要替妹妹完成这个梦想；Hebe则是想要赢得一万元的奖金，而Ella的梦想就是靠比赛挣的钱为家里买一个新沙发。</span></p>
<p><br></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="" data-copyright="0" data-ratio="0.5183585313174947" data-s="300,640" style="width:100%;height:auto" src="http://192.168.3.19:8900/api/base/imgproxy?1=1&siteid=1&url=https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/JFguiaeP3xaRZIjTYTuf4lQvcBNTG44pCmshcgOniavyPCWKdgGjub9iabtrwcCP3K4R2V3hsiaiaOvvbISV0E1fy3w/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="463" style=""></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 14px;">之前Ella接受采访的时候还打趣说发第一张专辑《女生宿舍》的时候还以为这也会是她们人生中的最后一张专辑，觉得自己注定会成为“一片歌手”。</span></p>
<p><br></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="" data-copyright="0" data-ratio="0.54421768707483" style="width:100%;height:auto" src="http://192.168.3.19:8900/api/base/imgproxy?1=1&siteid=1&url=https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/JFguiaeP3xaRZIjTYTuf4lQvcBNTG44pCwVYxSOVibGJF14ia2xcYAARRmZibRtWfNRlnU2W17h1b8icoUhCrJyEYDw/640?wx_fmt=gif" data-type="gif" data-w="441" style=""></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 14px;">但人生就是这样，越不期待什么就越来什么。SHE的第一张专辑《女生宿舍》仅在台湾就创造了近16万的销量，全亚洲的销量逼近75万张，主打歌《恋人未满》更是一直传唱至今。</span></p>
<p><br></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="" data-copyright="0" data-ratio="0.88" data-s="300,640" style="width:100%;height:auto" src="http://192.168.3.19:8900/api/base/imgproxy?1=1&siteid=1&url=https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/JFguiaeP3xaRZIjTYTuf4lQvcBNTG44pC2sWT9TedYGAj0vJ0Y6hOCgKLT4Guk0BErx6tFPW6USGM4qiaGoDVnPA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="400" style=""></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 14px;">2002年SHE顺势发了《青春株式社会》和《美丽新世界》两张专辑，其中由周杰伦和方文山联手打造的《热带雨林》也成了那一年的爆款歌曲。</span></p>
<p><br></p>
<p><img class="" data-ratio="0.86" style="width:100%;height:auto" src="http://192.168.3.19:8900/api/base/imgproxy?1=1&siteid=1&url=https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/JFguiaeP3xaRZIjTYTuf4lQvcBNTG44pCxjbTPicbrUoMrWFZCXxddYG7JuHFPJKIDySfm2dIrpUIf6fmXvOfJYA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="600" style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);display: block;width: 100%;height: auto;" data-backw="558" data-backh="480" data-before-oversubscription-url="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/JFguiaeP3xaRZIjTYTuf4lQvcBNTG44pCxjbTPicbrUoMrWFZCXxddYG7JuHFPJKIDySfm2dIrpUIf6fmXvOfJYA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg"></p>
<p><br></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 14px;">这两张专辑之后，三个人的风格定位也越来越明确。Selina就是留着长发爱哭爱爱笑的小公主，Hebe是高冷话不多的中长发酷女孩，活泼开朗的“假小子”Ella则成为了队内的“官方发言人”。</span></p>
<p><br></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="" data-copyright="0" data-ratio="0.54421768707483" style="width:100%;height:auto" src="http://192.168.3.19:8900/api/base/imgproxy?1=1&siteid=1&url=https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/JFguiaeP3xaRZIjTYTuf4lQvcBNTG44pCms2Ua9NcvxqBnqBntXfTclf3vp8joXJMRG6ibLNmec9P92lGLQ6xIfg/640?wx_fmt=gif" data-type="gif" data-w="441" style=""></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 14px;">2003年．SHE凭借《Super Star》登上了事业巅峰，毫不夸张地说，这首歌成了SHE所有歌曲中传唱度最高的一首，试问全国上下谁不会唱“你是电，你是光，你是唯一的神话”？</span></p>
<p><br></p>
<p><img class="" data-ratio="1.45179584120983" style="width:100%;height:auto" src="http://192.168.3.19:8900/api/base/imgproxy?1=1&siteid=1&url=https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/JFguiaeP3xaRZIjTYTuf4lQvcBNTG44pCMlhiaqFOYV0qdNGrLRspuxblaXJYEHsTNvMv44EFa8yVSoQBBy9Y55Q/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="529" style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);display: block;width: 100%;height: auto;" data-backw="529" data-backh="768" data-before-oversubscription-url="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/JFguiaeP3xaRZIjTYTuf4lQvcBNTG44pCMlhiaqFOYV0qdNGrLRspuxblaXJYEHsTNvMv44EFa8yVSoQBBy9Y55Q/640?wx_fmt=jpeg"></p>
<p><br></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 14px;">也是在《Super Star》时期，SHE经历了出道之后第一个比较大的坎。Ella因为主持节目出外景而出意外使背脊第一腰椎受伤，走路的时候必须要穿着背架保护背脊，所以只好暂时在家休养。</span></p>
<p><br></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="" data-copyright="0" data-ratio="0.6091370558375635" data-s="300,640" style="width:100%;height:auto" src="http://192.168.3.19:8900/api/base/imgproxy?1=1&siteid=1&url=https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/JFguiaeP3xaRZIjTYTuf4lQvcBNTG44pCqJyQ53NCUibZNZqjpOPHF0RovNW1xrO7zy13Mv7x9eXRib73LIbumxAQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="394" style=""></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 14px;">但这段时间正好和《Super Star》的宣传期相撞，所以这张专辑的一切宣传活动都只有Hebe和Selina两个人参加。</span></p>
<p><br></p>
<p><img class="" data-ratio="0.7516666666666667" style="width:100%;height:auto" src="http://192.168.3.19:8900/api/base/imgproxy?1=1&siteid=1&url=https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/JFguiaeP3xaRZIjTYTuf4lQvcBNTG44pCQ3qoiayC8WVsrJ6iamyBMLrPRs7Riazv57Z0ZqxGMqKyZhA2o0m7VQD9w/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="600" style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);display: block;width: 100%;height: auto;" data-backw="558" data-backh="419" data-before-oversubscription-url="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/JFguiaeP3xaRZIjTYTuf4lQvcBNTG44pCQ3qoiayC8WVsrJ6iamyBMLrPRs7Riazv57Z0ZqxGMqKyZhA2o0m7VQD9w/640?wx_fmt=jpeg"></p>
<p><br></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 14px;">好在Ella的因伤缺席没有影响《Super Star》的一路飙红，SHE也在次年凭借此专辑入围第15届台湾金曲奖最佳重唱组合奖。</span></p>
<p><br></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="" data-copyright="0" data-ratio="0.54421768707483" style="width:100%;height:auto" src="http://192.168.3.19:8900/api/base/imgproxy?1=1&siteid=1&url=https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/JFguiaeP3xaRZIjTYTuf4lQvcBNTG44pCQIshLnS8ibJIJS8YO2EzH35ZPtJb5tmKcwJsudfwSNCKbyMtBG7vuGw/640?wx_fmt=gif" data-type="gif" data-w="441" style=""></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 14px;">再之后，SHE一直保持着平均每年两张专辑的发专速度，接连发布了《不想长大》、《Play》和《SHERO》等多张大热专辑，更难得的是每一张专辑都能出至少一首传唱度极高的热门歌曲，比如《两个人的荒岛》、《半糖主义》、《不想长大》、《五月天》……每一首至今都是KTV的必点歌曲。</span></p>
<p><br></p>
<p><img class="" data-backh="349" data-backw="558" data-before-oversubscription-url="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/JFguiaeP3xaRZIjTYTuf4lQvcBNTG44pCKuHjYwkauhiaddUbQNnyR5dTJPeNg8DC6tUGAB7xF4Yn8fz17dq8ibicw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-oversubscription-url="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/JFguiaeP3xaRZIjTYTuf4lQvcBNTG44pCicg5jJupp1t5B5tu05yMNJB6PeCwetKOA8iaTlU7pYDwbQszia5w4nmIw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="0.625" style="width:100%;height:auto" src="http://192.168.3.19:8900/api/base/imgproxy?1=1&siteid=1&url=https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/JFguiaeP3xaRZIjTYTuf4lQvcBNTG44pCicg5jJupp1t5B5tu05yMNJB6PeCwetKOA8iaTlU7pYDwbQszia5w4nmIw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="600" style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);display: block;width: 100%;height: auto;"></p>
<p><br></p>
<p><img class="" data-ratio="0.66" style="width:100%;height:auto" src="http://192.168.3.19:8900/api/base/imgproxy?1=1&siteid=1&url=https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/JFguiaeP3xaRZIjTYTuf4lQvcBNTG44pCllthIdcJeruWnsEQtZpNibj0mUCX45pF3iaLpBQAVjuQuqK7ibUQynHDg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="600" style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);display: block;width: 100%;height: auto;" data-backw="558" data-backh="368" data-before-oversubscription-url="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/JFguiaeP3xaRZIjTYTuf4lQvcBNTG44pCllthIdcJeruWnsEQtZpNibj0mUCX45pF3iaLpBQAVjuQuqK7ibUQynHDg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg"></p>
<p><br></p>
<section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section class="V5" style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;padding-left: 6px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="background-color: rgb(255, 129, 36);padding-right: 6px;padding-left: 6px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">我们单飞不解散</strong></p></section><section style="margin-top: -9px;margin-left: -6px;border-left: 2px solid rgb(13, 0, 21);border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(13, 0, 21);height: 16px;width: 16px;border-top-color: rgb(13, 0, 21);border-right-color: rgb(13, 0, 21);box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section></section></section></section><p class="pictext"><br></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 14px;">不过爆红如SHE也没能逃脱“合久必分，分久必合”的魔咒，2010年发布完新专辑《SHERO》之后，SHE正式宣布单飞不解散。</span></p>
<p><br></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="" data-copyright="0" data-ratio="0.54421768707483" style="width:100%;height:auto" src="http://192.168.3.19:8900/api/base/imgproxy?1=1&siteid=1&url=https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/JFguiaeP3xaRZIjTYTuf4lQvcBNTG44pCWbaVPP6kvf1elhgabmx04Gxj3Tl1icPsh387YsgPsSrOVl4IiaHwQJBw/640?wx_fmt=gif" data-type="gif" data-w="441" style=""></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 14px;">其实出道十年，三个人也更加明确了自己的喜好。有人更喜欢唱歌，有人更喜欢演戏，还有人觉得主持综艺更适合自己，所以分开发展自己更喜欢的事业也是情理之中的事。</span></p>
<p><br></p>
